item.title: [WFLY-6471] IIOPSslInvocationTestCase fails once -Dnode0 and -Dnode1 are used
item.description:
Description of problem:

  • IIOPSslInvocationTestCase fails once -Dnode0 and -Dnode1 are different. This test pass, once -Dnode0 and -Dnode1 are same.
  • IIOPSslInvocationTestCase was added by JBEAP-3502
  • Jenkins job run with same value of node0 and node1
  • Jenkins job run with different value of node0 and node1

How reproducible:
Always

Steps to Reproduce:

  1. EAP_HOME=...
  2. REPO=...
  3. ./integration-tests.sh -Dmaven.repo.local=$REPO -fae -Dmaven.test.failure.ignore=true -Dnode0=$MYTESTIP_1 -Dnode1=$MYTESTIP_2 -Djboss.dist=$ {EAP_HOME}

    -Dts.iiop -Dts.noSmoke -Dtest=IIOPSslInvocationTestCase -DfailIfNoTests=false -DtestLogToFile=false
